WEBVTT

00:05:29.617 --> 00:05:32.457
about the deep history
and craftsmanship of rugs.

00:05:32.481 --> 00:05:34.601
Sure, it helped him sell more rugs,

00:05:34.625 --> 00:05:36.712
but it also helped him
connect with people.

00:05:38.288 --> 00:05:41.784
Research shows that mastering your craft
helps you build connections.

00:05:41.808 --> 00:05:43.768
Take a study within hospitals.

00:05:43.792 --> 00:05:46.260
Radiologists who were
experts at their jobs

00:05:46.284 --> 00:05:49.462
ended up making more new friends at work
over the next nine months.

00:05:49.796 --> 00:05:52.074
And they occupied
more influential positions

00:05:52.098 --> 00:05:53.742
in their hospital networks.

00:05:54.454 --> 00:05:56.613
This is true in any line of work.

00:05:56.637 --> 00:05:57.788
Think about it.

00:05:57.812 --> 00:06:00.006
You love having mavens in your network: